Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The return of Ross Perot and US social concerns
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjvl8
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Aug 1996
The return of Ross Perot as a presidential candidate, the prohibition of third-trimester abortions, the proliferation of guns and the education of children about global warming.